 public boolVtiful\Kernel\Excel::iterateCharts
 callablecallable
 stringnullsheet&null;

Invokes the given callback once for each chart on a worksheet of the workbook currently open for reading. The callback receives an array describing the chart type, title, anchor and series; returning &false; from the callback stops the iteration.
